Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:13.294 --> 00:00:15.294
Today, we are making "Sizzling Mushrooms".

00:00:41.430 --> 00:00:43.430
Heat a sizzler plate over an open flame till it is red hot.

00:00:46.098 --> 00:00:48.098
Heat the oil on the plate.

00:00:59.886 --> 00:01:01.886
Add the onions and sauté on a medium flame for 2 to 3 minutes.

00:01:18.318 --> 00:01:20.318
Add the tomatoes.

00:01:32.884 --> 00:01:34.884
Add the mushrooms.

00:01:43.098 --> 00:01:45.100
Add salt to taste.

00:01:54.129 --> 00:01:56.130
Add the oregano.

00:01:57.395 --> 00:01:59.400
Add the chilli flakes.

00:01:59.191 --> 00:02:01.190
Add the cornflour.

00:02:04.286 --> 00:02:06.290
Mix well and sauté on a medium flame for 2 to 3 minutes.

00:02:31.181 --> 00:02:33.180
Place the plate on a wooden tray and serve immediately with toasted bread triangles.

